Stock Watchlist - COVID-19/Oil Price

Index and Stock price development 2020. Highlighted grey area indicates time span when markets reacted on the news of significant SARS-CoV-2 spread in northern Italy. Second highligted grey area indicated when markets reacted on the news of OPEC deal failure with Russia and resulting Saudi driven oil price war. For stock symbol legend see bottom of page. Most stocks in Biotech reached their highpoint just before news about a possible SARS driven recession hit the markets. Moderna and Arcturus gained positive momentum after initial price drop. Both companies develop RNA based therapeutics including potential SARS-CoV-2 vaccines. Moderna’s advantage seems to be a quickly scalable production platform whereas Arcturus’s approach might be superior due to smaller amounts of input RNA rnaitherapeutics.blogspot.com.

Stock price development in relation to individal highpoint of the indicated time span in the first plot is displayed.

Most recent stock price (24 March, 2020) in relation to possible beginning recession fear time span highpoint. E.g. Bionano lost around 60% of its price until now.
